  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ff771ccdf4150419d9ff4d342b069aae, type: 3}
  m_Name: Page_02
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Tutorials.Core.Editor::Unity.Tutorials.Core.Editor.TutorialPage
  Title:
    m_Untranslated: 
  m_Paragraphs:
    m_Items:
    - m_Type: 0
      Title:
        m_Untranslated: Plant Lifecycle
      Text:
        m_Untranslated: "Open the <b>Plant</b> prefab.\n\n<b>Steps:</b>\n1. Create
          a new <b>LifecycleData</b> asset:\n   <b>Create \u203A Ludocore \u203A
          Lifecycle Data</b>, name it <b>PlantData</b>\n\n2. Set short-lived values:\n  
          \u2022 startingEnergy \u2192 <b>50</b>\n   \u2022 maxEnergy \u2192 <b>50</b>\n  
          \u2022 energyDecayRate \u2192 <b>7</b>\n\n3. On the Plant prefab, Add Component:
          <b>Lifecycle</b>\n4. Assign <b>PlantData</b> to the lifecycleData field\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nPlants
          start at full energy and decay in about 7 seconds. They have no EnergyProvider
          \u2014 no growth, only fading."
      m_CodeSample: 
